Cohort
  Start date, end date
  Lessons
    title, notes
  Shirts
    name

  As a user I shouldnt be offered a shirt if I've worn it while a cohort is happening
  As a user I should be able to wear a shirt
  As a user I should be to identify a potential wear activity between a shirt and a lesson


Cohort => Lessons
Lesson <=> Shirts join wear_opportunities
Shirt => Wearings (Can't be worn again while cohort is happening)
Cohort => Wearings

  
